{"type": "article", "id": 6973, "title": "Asmara 小火炉", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-02T07:39:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234147zDk5pC0TNlQtKrZU.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t德国设计公司 Hase Kaminofenbau GmbH 带来的这款小火炉的外表纤细修长，其四周用料是陶瓷，因此可以在内部熊熊燃烧中保持外表的“高冷”。小火炉的三面设置玻璃，方便观察火焰状况，加柴口较高，方便添加柴火，且有助于用户的安全。其进气口和灰烬抽屉被放置在整个装置的下方，以保证外表的美观。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341464ucXi10HJ8hA6jsl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234146Od4ZvNi5sE10KCg2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}